  "body": "# 🖼️ Little Item frames\n\n## ✨ Description  \nThis resource pack makes **item frames smaller**, so they take up **less visual space** and look **cleaner and more compact**.  \nPerfect for decorative builds, redstone setups, or minimalist bases.\n\n## ⚙️ Features  \n- Reduced size for all item frames  \n- Works with both normal and glow item frames  \n- No texture changes to items inside the frames  \n- Fully compatible with most other texture packs  \n\n## 🧩 Compatibility  \n- **Minecraft Versions:** 1.20 – 1.21  \n- **Works with:** OptiFine, Sodium, Iris  \n- No mod dependencies  \n\n## 📦 Installation  \n1. Download the `.zip` file.  \n2. Place it into your resourcepacks folder:  \n\n",
